metadata.name: Captain's Lounge Access Passport
metadata.description: Captain's Lounge Access Passport holder is eligible for 5 presale whitelisted spots in every NFT collection, next in line for BotsDAO membership, exclusive airdrops, ability to retain level 20 of OG Bot on max level re-mint, receive a share of 1% of secondary sales, Captain discord role and in game title, and more.
